      <description>&lt;p&gt;Looking to simplify testing in your &lt;a href=&#34;https://angular.io&#34;&gt;Angular&lt;/a&gt; 19 monorepo and integrate it with &lt;a href=&#34;https://neovim.io&#34;&gt;Neovim&lt;/a&gt;? This guide will show you how to set up &lt;a href=&#34;https://jestjs.io&#34;&gt;Jest&lt;/a&gt;, configure Angular for Jest, and use &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/nvim-neotest/neotest&#34;&gt;Neotest&lt;/a&gt; with the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/haydenmeade/neotest-jest&#34;&gt;neotest-jest adapter&lt;/a&gt; to run tests directly in your editor.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;demo--source-code&#34;&gt;Demo &amp;amp; Source Code&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;iframe allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen&#34; loading=&#34;eager&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;strict-origin-when-cross-origin&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/bgFl-oWfmYo?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;&#34; title=&#34;YouTube video&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here is the source code for the sample app used in this guide: &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/konstantindenerz/article-angular-jest-neovim-setup&#34;&gt;GitHub Repo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
